flowchart TD
  %% =========  LEGEND / CLUSTERS  =========
  subgraph Simulation Loop
    direction LR
    S1[Generate scenario‑specific<br/>ServerTx list] -->|push| Mempool
    Mempool -. consumes .-> ProcessBlock
  end

  subgraph ProcessBlock
    direction TB
    PB1[processMempool<br/>write-ahead log<br/>+ error collection] --> PB2[processServerTx<br/>for each tx]
    PB2 --> PB3[update lastProcessedHeight]
    PB3 --> PB4[store block record<br/>LevelDB blocks]
    PB4 --> PB5[maybe archiveSnapshot<br/>LevelDB archive & refs]
    PB5 --> PB6[routeMessages to new ServerTx]
    PB6 --> PB7[autoProposeSingleSigners to new ServerTx]
    PB7 -->|push| Mempool
    PB1 -.->|CollectedResult| EC[ErrorCollector<br/>tracks severity & context]
    EC -.->|critical errors| STOP[Stop Processing]
  end

  subgraph processServerTx
    direction TB
    ST1[isSignerAuthorized?] --> ST2[get entity+meta]
    ST2 --> ST3[processEntityInput]
    ST3 --> ST4[update signers map<br/>& collect OutboxMsg array]
    ST3 -.->|Result<T,E>| ST5[Error handling<br/>with ProcessingError]
  end

  %% =========  processEntityInput cases =========
  subgraph processEntityInput
    direction TB
    IE_add[add_tx<br/>→ append to entity.mempool]:::green
    IE_prop[propose_block<br/>single‑signer → apply<br/>multi‑signer → broadcast]:::yellow
    IE_app[approve_block<br/>→ track quorum,<br/>maybe enqueue commit]:::yellow
    IE_comm[commit_block<br/>→ apply txs,<br/>generate transfer msgs]:::green
  end

  %% =========  Storage subsystem =========
  subgraph Storage LevelDB namespaces
    direction LR
    STstate[(state)]:::store
    STwal[(wal)]:::store
    STblocks[(blocks)]:::store
    STarchive[(archive)]:::store
    STrefs[(refs)]:::store
  end

  %% =========  Data flow edges =========
  ProcessBlock -->|WAL put/get| STwal
  ProcessBlock -->|block put/get| STblocks
  ProcessBlock -->|archive put/get| STarchive
  ProcessBlock -->|ref HEAD| STrefs
  saveSnapshot --> STstate
  recoverServer --> STstate
  recoverServer --> STwal
  recoverServer --> STarchive
  recoverServer --> STrefs

  %% =========  Start‑up / Recovery =========
  subgraph Startup / Recovery
    direction TB
    R1[initializeServer OR<br/>loadSnapshot] --> R2[replay registry WAL]
    R2 --> R3[replay tx WAL → mempool]
    R3 -->|if mempool not empty| ProcessBlock
  end

  %% =========  Type Safety =========
  subgraph Type System
    direction LR
    TS1[Branded Types<br/>EntityId, SignerIdx, etc] --> TS2[Type Helpers<br/>parseSignerIdx, etc]
    TS2 --> TS3[Result Types<br/>Ok/Err handling]
  end

  %% =========  Styles =========
  classDef store fill:#e7f1ff,stroke:#2f72d6;
  classDef green fill:#d4f4dd,stroke:#20882d;
  classDef yellow fill:#fff8dc,stroke:#b58900;
